{"tid":390953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得中大港獨海報會係另一次運動嘅開始？","createTime":"2017-09-07T12:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T00:22:44.000Z","uid":7109,"like":247,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad801db1b60f336476a826329dea83ef8ed4f6d6","tid":390953,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"記唔記得2014年雨傘運動係點嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近因由 9月大專生罷課 -&gt; 中學生罷課-&gt; 遊行 -&gt; 鎮壓<br />\n而遠因就係佔領中環運動, 政改問題<br />\n<br />\n今次中大掛banner嘅事影響越來越大, 唔單止中大校方反應比以前大, 甚至黑警話適當時會執法乜乜乜，即管睇下林奠會點回應<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得當年港大示威, 有警察入校執法造成好大嘅迴響。而呢次牽涉到香港獨立同學生自主嘅問題, 中大校方如果強硬回應, 清場甚至由警察嚟執行，對中大嘅衝擊係前所未見。跟住落嚟就好睇中大學生會點反應，我覺得肯強硬回應，罷課等等，一定會比港大當年得到更多回響, 爭取更多大學大専肯支持, 再有一次全港性嘅學生運動。<br />\n本士派再搞下包圍行動等等,成件事會好唔同, 升級機會更大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然講到呢到, 成件事都好缺乏一件好大嘅「遠因」, 未必會如當年一般咁浩蕩，但至少唔會係一件小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中大巴絲打請加油"},{"pid":"632928d436de757ad3e823a83708a7b3f0b1fd82","tid":390953,"uid":130247,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohhwef0GQQt24XLEI/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ohhwef0GQQt24XLEI%2Fgiphy.gif&h=da447209&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b0cf09e44a2380e484267877f2c68bf7ed03159","tid":390953,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"678449b9a6939646f00379ea6e9a3822fdf3e0cd","tid":390953,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:04:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0c16d09a59810b967936d680e964ef1e24c6dd6","tid":390953,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea130a70d2431b067241d9dbb3be76aeff9f7b83","tid":390953,"uid":7109,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohhwef0GQQt24XLEI/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ohhwef0GQQt24XLEI%2Fgiphy.gif&h=da447209&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果件事要搞大就一定係著眼於 學術自由 上，先係鼓動人民最好嘅論點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140a489b8fe1744a1003a84cda5464a4ca6cba2e","tid":390953,"uid":7109,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:06:47.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係讀中大，但請你地加油，積極揾其他大學幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489cdf240c8008fb49c2e3839e29c8ce0e0c630a","tid":390953,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:07:56.000Z","msg":"普選幻滅, 13+3落鑊, 香港依家已經係講獨立"},{"pid":"e5bc791a63241fbb0940be75bc8f2acd826e005c","tid":390953,"uid":121958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:08:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442113084dbdbcb83ce498aed06eacf61b53fa77","tid":390953,"uid":54876,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"講真，十劃未有一撇<br />\n<br />\n不過聚番啲人氣都好"},{"pid":"3ff18f28b6357deba20a5ec48a0154f879dd06e9","tid":390953,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真，十劃未有一撇<br />\n<br />\n不過聚番啲人氣都好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但如果仲係「運動」, 就真係無進步啦"},{"pid":"40e8c9ab08bad9e77cfc12f9b1e934870c6aa15f","tid":390953,"uid":121958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真，十劃未有一撇<br />\n<br />\n不過聚番啲人氣都好</blockquote><br />\n好多時候都唔係安排得嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有邊個估到會射催淚彈？ 唔係射咗催淚彈未必有14年嘅運動出現"},{"pid":"06644cb34a3002e04ba294b41a770f768709f963","tid":390953,"uid":121958