gree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f67099f643306f509c44f7c950c5bd3a21f179","tid":390953,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基本法第27條保障言論自由<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》第二十七條規定，香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。據了解，聯署的醫生諮詢法律意見後，認為醫委會專業守則限制醫生自我宣傳的條文，可能違反上述《基本法》保障港人的權利，並可能牴觸人權法，<span style=\"color: red;\">法律意見又指言論自由應只在涉及誹謗、危害國家安全或社會秩序時才受限制</span>，醫生宣揚個人資料應不受此限。&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20051007/5289906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20051007%2F5289906&d=8IT2q3P%2Bda4EDq8PYwT7BCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=3db17406\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20051007%2F5289906&h=1b0f48f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20051007/5289906</a><br />\n<br />\n最終又釋法？</blockquote><br />\n噓國歌都加咗條<br />\n跟手又加條新例姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1979bf51707bce833658e53889f70ed597c48b9d","tid":390953,"uid":139142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:09:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪又係貼下海報 掛下banner 打下嘴炮<br />\n激進啲咪搞多次佔中、衝下垃圾會 坐返一碌半碌 上下bbc咁囉<br />\n好多學生根本就係too simple sometimes na&iuml;ve <br />\n搞港獨最需要嘅智慧 手段 計謀 而唔係橫衝直撞之後俾人拉<br />\n<br />\n純粹個人睇法 <br />\n利申：支持香港獨立</blockquote><br />\n咁你有咩高見去抗爭?<br />\n願聞其詳 你既智慧 手段 計謀"},{"pid":"aeaf385d6a3243e1d1f2c8fe62f9f1a8bc4b1d6b","tid":390953,"uid":60749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:10:44.000Z","msg":"遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae78ce2a8122501341793dc7e6dbd9b55ab3bec","tid":390953,"uid":60749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquot