,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港的希望"},{"pid":"7237ae502710ec712a1e935b802e7640aeb2d855","tid":390953,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:18:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7da3525c49a9f7a808794aa2f4275c91d1e2884e","tid":390953,"uid":120156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:27:29.000Z","msg":"呢個時候真係想要番學聯 一間大學自己其實搞唔掂"},{"pid":"291c3a5d77c956f3a01923b9e6b408cae7993868","tid":390953,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個時候真係想要番學聯 一間大學自己其實搞唔掂</blockquote><br />\n自治八樓，資產，抽稅權。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5494ce6d7ef99d7b60b8dc5c978a97c70bd72c82","tid":390953,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:23:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"148dd1530ac2e80c7b988caa927aaf375b4db600","tid":390953,"uid":134665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:10:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b55f3a3f77e6d89637bdc15bf1f34a68b4527f","tid":390953,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T19:00:30.000Z","msg":"咩"},{"pid":"2dbc9dcdf1f2143849e6a782a1ea8506a887cd9b","tid":390953,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T19:20:34.000Z","msg":"成個背景無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個時有政改議題+戴妖9吹搞局<br />\n比佢吹吹下又屎忽撞棍搞左大壇野出黎。"},{"pid":"5e972b53880a51ee1338ee5115b072085403758c","tid":390953,"uid":120369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T20:26:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記唔記得2014年雨傘運動係點嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近因由 9月大專生罷課 -&gt; 中學生罷課-&gt; 遊行 -&gt; 鎮壓<br />\n而遠因就係佔領中環運動, 政改問題<br />\n<br />\n今次中大掛banner嘅事影響越來越大, 唔單止中大校方反應比以前大, 甚至黑警話適當時會執法乜乜乜，即管睇下林奠會點回應<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得當年港大示威, 有警察入校執法造成好大嘅迴響。而呢次牽涉到香港獨立同學生自主嘅問題, 中大校方如果強硬回應, 清場甚至由警察嚟執行，對中大嘅衝擊係前所未見。跟住落嚟就好睇中大學生會點反應，我覺得肯強硬回應，罷課等等，一定會比港大當年得到更多回響, 爭取更多大學大専肯支持, 再有一次全港性嘅學生運動。<br />\n本士派再搞下包圍行動等等,成件事會好唔同, 升級機會更大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然講到呢到, 成件事都好缺乏一件好大嘅「遠因」, 未必會如當年一般咁浩蕩，但至少唔會係一件小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中大巴絲打請加油</blockquote><br />\n唔覺"},{"pid":"95fb74a158ef115172f523cb57f9551cd268cdd1","tid":390953,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e9f5e3f7c7c09e73c93b0de7d0977959f9b851","tid":390953,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:04:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成個背景無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個時有政改議題+戴妖9吹搞局<br />\n比佢吹吹下又屎忽撞棍搞左大壇野出黎。</blockquote><br />\n民族發明就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多野都望落似突發咁"},{"pid":"4c9dc10e808eaebec282eca89f9888524f88c9f3","tid":390953,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:05:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fe989ec0f0dc93c47ac7fef29844d649cb150694","tid":390953,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}